{"ID":270364, "Text":"<div class=\"page\"><div class=\"pageNum\"><a name=\"364\"><\/a><div class=\"prev\"><a href=\"stpjs363.html\">Prev<\/a><\/div><div class=\"next\"><a href=\"stpjs365.html\">Next<\/a><\/div>\n\t\t\t    STPJS 364<\/div>\n  <div class=\"topic \">President Joseph Smith&rsquo;s Address&mdash;Defense of His Prophetic<\/div>\n  <div class=\"topic \">Calling&mdash;Resurrection of the Dead&mdash;Fulness of Ordinances<\/div>\n  <div class=\"topic \">Necessary Both for the Living and Dead<\/div>\n  <p class=\"std\">The Savior has the words of eternal life.<span class=\"footRef\">1<\/span> Nothing else can profit us. There is no salvation in\n  believing an evil report against our neighbor.<span class=\"footRef\">2<\/span> I advise all to go on to perfection,<span class=\"footRef\">3<\/span> and search deeper<span class=\"footRef\">4<\/span>\n  and deeper into the mysteries of Godliness.<span class=\"footRef\">5<\/span> A man can do nothing for himself<span class=\"footRef\">6<\/span> unless God direct\n  him<span class=\"footRef\">7<\/span> in the right way; and the Priesthood is for that purpose.<\/p>\n  <p class=\"std\">The last time I spoke on this stand it was on the resurrection of the dead, when I promised to\n  continue my remarks upon that subject. I still feel a desire to say something on this subject. Let us\n  this very day begin anew, and now say, with all our hearts,<span class=\"footRef\">8<\/span> we will forsake our sins and be\n  righteous.<span class=\"footRef\">9<\/span> I shall read the 24th chapter of Matthew,<span class=\"footRef\">10<\/span> and give it a literal rendering and reading; and\n  when it is rightly understood, it will be edifying.<\/p>\n  <p class=\"std\">I thought the very oddity of its rendering would be edifying anyhow&mdash;&ldquo;And it will preached be,\n  the Gospel of the kingdom, in the whole world, to a witness<span class=\"footRef\">11<\/span> over all people: and then will the end\n  come.&rdquo;<span class=\"footRef\">12<\/span> I will now read it in German [which he did, and many Germans who were present said he\n  translated it correctly].<\/p>\n  <div class=\"topic \">Interpretation of Scripture<\/div>\n  <p class=\"std\">The Savior said when these tribulations<span class=\"footRef\">13<\/span> should take place, it should be committed to a man<span class=\"footRef\">14<\/span>\n  who should be a witness over the whole world: the keys of knowledge, power and revelations<span class=\"footRef\">15<\/span>\n  should be revealed to a witness who should hold the testimony to the world. It has always been my\n  province to dig up hidden mysteries<span class=\"footRef\">16<\/span>&mdash;new things&mdash;for my hearers. Just at the time when some men\n  think that I have no right to the keys of the Priesthood<span class=\"footRef\">17<\/span>&mdash;just at that time I have the greatest right.\n  The Germans are an exalted people. The old German translators are the most nearly correct&mdash;most\n  honest of any of the translators; and therefore I get testimony to bear me out in the revelations that\n  I have preached for the last fourteen years. The old German, Latin, Greek and Hebrew translations\n  all say it is true: they cannot be impeached,<span class=\"footRef\">18<\/span> and therefore I am in good company.<\/p>\n  <p class=\"std\">All the testimony is that the Lord in the last days would commit the keys of the Priesthood to\n  a witness over all people.<span class=\"footRef\">19<\/span><\/p>\n  <div class=\"footnotes\">\n    <div class=\"footnote\">1. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"108706\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 108706)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(108706)\">John 6:68<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">2. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"113744\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 113744)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(113744)\">D&amp;C 42:27<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">3. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"110171\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 110171)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(110171)\">Heb. 6:1<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">4. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"109427\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 109427)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(109427)\">1 Cor. 2:10<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">5. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"110007\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 110007)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(110007)\">1 Tim. 3:16<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"113294\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 113294)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(113294)\">D&amp;C 19:10<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">6. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"106874\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 106874)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(106874)\">Ps. 127:1<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"108674\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 108674)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(108674)\">John 5:19,30<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"108720\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 108720)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(108720)\">John 8:28<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"108820\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 108820)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(108820)\">John 15:5<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">7. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"109937\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 109937)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(109937)\">1 Thes. 3:11<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">8. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"111690\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 111690)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(111690)\">Mosiah 21:35<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"115146\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 115146)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(115146)\">D&amp;C 98:47<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">9. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"111576\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 111576)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(111576)\">Mosiah 5:5<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"112018\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 112018)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(112018)\">Alma 22:18<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"112255\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 112255)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(112255)\">Alma 39:9<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"112542\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 112542)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(112542)\">3 Ne. 5:3<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"114099\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 114099)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(114099)\">D&amp;C 58:43<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">10. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"108196\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 108196)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(108196)\">Matt. 24:1-51<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">11. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"107242\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 107242)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(107242)\">Isa. 55:4<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">12. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"108206\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 108206)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(108206)\">Matt. 24:14<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"117086\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 117086)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(117086)\">JS&mdash;M 1:31<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">13. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"108209\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 108209)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(108209)\">Matt. 24:21,29<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">14. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"108207\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 108207)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(108207)\">Matt. 24:14<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">15. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"113504\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 113504)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(113504)\">D&amp;C 28:7<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"114638\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 114638)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(114638)\">D&amp;C 84:19<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"115421\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 115421)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(115421)\">D&amp;C 107:18<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"116155\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 116155)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(116155)\">D&amp;C 128:14,21<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"116336\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 116336)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(116336)\">D&amp;C 132:7,19,39,45,59,64<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">16. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"109425\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 109425)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(109425)\">1 Cor. 2:7<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"114384\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 114384)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(114384)\">D&amp;C 76:7<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"114529\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 114529)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(114529)\">D&amp;C 77:6<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">17. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"114314\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 114314)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(114314)\">D&amp;C 68:17-18<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"115415\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 115415)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(115415)\">D&amp;C 107:16,76<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"115703\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 115703)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(115703)\">D&amp;C 113:8<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"115757\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 115757)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(115757)\">D&amp;C 121:21<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"116996\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 116996)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(116996)\">Abr. 1:27,31<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"117011\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 117011)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(117011)\">Abr. 2:11<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">18. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"114319\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 114319)\">&nbsp;<\/